==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coble
<hw>Co"ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>cuopel</ets>;
cf. W. <ets>ceubal</ets> skiff, ferryboat.]</ety> <def>A flat-floored
fishing boat with a lug sail, and a drop rudder extending from two to
four feet below the keel. It was originally used on the stormy coast of
Yorkshire, England.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

